```

☝️ i think this is what is causing the problem

Updated setup.py to use extras_require to differentiate between python 2 and python 3 requirements.  This gets along with pipenv. Fixes #142 

Now pipenv users may add some additional specifications to their Pipfile to get the correct versions installed consistently.

```
[packages]
social-auth-core = "*"
python-openid = {version=">=2.2.5", markers="python_version<'3.0'"}
python3-openid = {version=">=3.0.10", markers="python_version>='3.0'"}
defusedxml = {version=">=0.5.0rc1", markers="python_version>='3.0'"}
```
